Superstar Nigerian singer, Innocent Idibia, popularly known as 2baba took to his social media to appreciate a student who used his songs for his final year project.
2baba who reposted a picture showing the hardcover of the student’s final year project disclosed that the student’s effort was highly appreciated.
The student’s project which was written in 2018 and titled music as a platform for social commentary made use of 2baba’s Holy Holy, One Love, E be like say and hold my hand.
Reacting to the final year thesis, 2baba wrote:
Highly appreciated. All the best. Reposted from @djlasgidi95 This Project Work Is Dedicated To @official2baba #WARRIORS #20yrs#GRATEFUL